headline: Intuit QuickBooks and the Professional Women’s Hockey League Announce Multi-year Canadian Partnership
summary: TORONTO, December 12, 2024--Intuit Inc. (Nasdaq: INTU), the global financial technology platform that makes Intuit TurboTax, Credit Karma, QuickBooks, and Mailchimp, today announced that it has entered into a multi-year partnership across Canada with the Professional Women’s Hockey League (PWHL), naming Intuit QuickBooks as the league's Official Accounting Software Partner.
